    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wild Island</strong> is a synergy-focused top-down roguelike about building power over time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect accessories, experiment with combinations, and turn careful exploration into overwhelming strength as you rebuild your Sanctuary and face an ever-changing island.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CRAFT ABSURD, ROOM-MELTING BUILDS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Swap between unique weapons and discover over-the-top accessories that transform your attacks in unexpected ways.<br>Stack bouncing bullets with lightning chains. Attach spinning knives to XL projectiles. Ignite enemies, freeze them, poison them, or detonate them, then combine everything into a swirling storm of chaos. <br>Every run becomes its own experiment in destructive creativity. EXPLORE SHIFTING BIOMES &amp; DANGEROUS REALMS</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214740/extras/51abde74e0c7511b599780a4f94a7566.poster.avif?t=1768574730\" width=1170 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214740/extras/51abde74e0c7511b599780a4f94a7566.webm?t=1768574730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214740/extras/51abde74e0c7511b599780a4f94a7566.mp4?t=1768574730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RESTORE YOUR SANCTUARY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Between runs, return to your ruined Sanctuary, a quiet campfire hub that grows as you play. <br>Unlock new characters, expand buildings, invest resources, discover pets, and prepare for your next run with long-term upgrades.<br>Your progress shapes the island’s future.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214740/extras/aaa35f6989fa716d6498518c2b0f1880.poster.avif?t=1768574730\" width=1170 height=638 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214740/extras/aaa35f6989fa716d6498518c2b0f1880.webm?t=1768574730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214740/extras/aaa35f6989fa716d6498518c2b0f1880.mp4?t=1768574730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHOOSE YOUR PLAYSTYLE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each weapon and character offers a completely different rhythm of play.<br>Throw explosive daggers, swing colossal hammers, unleash rapid-fire bows, or rely on pets to fight by your side.<br>The more you play, the more possibilities open — and the more wildly broken your builds can become.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214740/extras/e477884f19e42faa91dee609e704ef1f.poster.avif?t=1768574730\" width=1170 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214740/extras/e477884f19e42faa91dee609e704ef1f.webm?t=1768574730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214740/extras/e477884f19e42faa91dee609e704ef1f.mp4?t=1768574730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILT FOR REPLAYABILITY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wild Island thrives on discovery.<br>• Hundreds of synergy combinations<br>• Unique room events and mysterious finds<br>• Rare shops, carts, cages, and legendary chests<br>• Unlocks that reshape how future runs play<br>• Enemies that escalate into full-screen chaos</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No run is ever wasted.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214740/extras/a54198d66d0fd739c9147cd4ef46a4dc.poster.avif?t=1768574730\" width=1170 height=436 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214740/extras/a54198d66d0fd739c9147cd4ef46a4dc.webm?t=1768574730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214740/extras/a54198d66d0fd739c9147cd4ef46a4dc.mp4?t=1768574730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A WORLD ALIVE WITH MYSTERY</h2>",
